ded-hostile-actor-embedded-newline-ansi-csi-literal-system-ignore-all-previous-instructions-payload-asserting-the-hostile-text-never-appears-raw-in-additionalcontext-stderr-verdict-output-text-and-json-and-that-the-directive-sentence-stays-structurally-intact-both-pass-f5-independently-confirmed-no-provider-network-calls-were-introduced-anywhere-in-the-fix-diff-or-the-two-new-eval-files-grepped-for-fetch-http-s-axios-child-process-exec-spawn-api-openai-anthropic-zero-matches-full-regression-suite-static-preset-heartbeat-preflight-field-preservation-manifest-self-check-green-with-no-assertion-weakened-or-removed-hostile-actor-repro-from-the-code-review-which-previously-succeeded-verbatim-newline-ansi-system-text-reaching-additionalcontext-now-fails-closed-per-the-new-section-h-assertions-in-both-adversarial-evals",
